## ğŸ“˜ Project 1: Average Calculator

### ğŸ§© Description
The **Average Calculator** program allows users to input multiple numbers and calculates their average.  
It demonstrates:
- Input handling (via Scanner)
- Loops and conditionals
- Basic arithmetic operations
- Exception handling (optional)

### âš™ï¸ Features
- Accepts dynamic number of inputs  
- Calculates and displays the average  
- Handles invalid (non-numeric) input gracefully  

