## ğŸ“˜ Project 2: Student List

### ğŸ§© Description
The **Student List** program manages a list of students and their details such as name, ID, and marks.  
It demonstrates:
- Class and object creation  
- ArrayList and collection usage  
- Encapsulation and object manipulation  

### âš™ï¸ Features
- Add new students  
- Display all students  
- Search for a student by ID or name  
- (Optional) Remove or update student details  

